---
import "../styles.css";
import Button2 from "./Button2.astro";
---

<section class="membership">
  <img src="/img/membership.webp" alt="membership-billede" />
  <div class="text-box">
    <h2>Membership</h2>
    <p>Apply for membership by signing up in our online "Lobby". It is both free and non-binding.</p>
    <div class="button"><a href="/login"><Button2 buttontext="Sign up" /></a></div>
</div>
</section>
<section class="text_columns">
  <div class="col2_text">
    <p>The Lobby is not a waiting list, and allocation of memberships is done through a random selection based on our diversity criteria.</p>
    <p>We aim for a diverse representation of our society in our bath club, believing that it contributes to an inclusive and open community. A Glaecier membership provides access to our facilities during opening hours.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .membership {
    background-color: var(--background);
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    height: 800px;
  }
  .membership img {
    height: 800px;
    object-fit: cover;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .text-box {
    margin: 3rem;
  }
  .membership p {
    font-size: var(--p-font-size);
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  .membership h2 {
    font-size: var(--h2-font-size);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
</style>
